name: CYMBALTA 30 MG
treatmentDescriptions: Cymbalta is indicated for the treatment of major depressive episodes.- Cymbalta is indicated for the management of neuropathic pain associated with diabetic peripheral neuropathy.- Cymbalta is indicated for the treatment of generalized anxiety disorder (GAD).- Cymbalta is indicated for the management of fibromyalgia.- Cymbalta is indicated for the management of chronic muscoskeletal pain when other therapies have failed or are contra-indicated. This has been established in studies in patients with chronic low back pain (CLBP) and chronic pain due to osteoarthritis.
warnings: תרופה מוגבלת לרישום ע'י רופא מומחה או הגבלה אחרת
